{
 "name": "RPlog_Rescue_of_Danik_Kreldin",
 "title": "Rescue of Danik Kreldin",
 "summary": "Aboard an Imperial vessel, pilots and officers gather on the Berth Deck for a briefing on a daring mission to rescue the captured Admiral Danik Kreldin, who alerted the Imperial fleet to his location on Tatooine before contact was lost. The ace Krieg takes notes alongside the brooding pilot Seifer Wolf, the Intelligence officer Dimitri, the retired Colonel Bogumil, and others, as command reveals a task force being built around the HIMS Malevolence and the Dauntless. With no resistance expected in space, the plan calls for an immediate ground assault to retrieve the Advisor. The briefing sets the Imperial rescue effort in motion.",
